def firstAndLast(s):
    first_letter=s[0]
    length=len[s]
    last_letter=s[length-1]
    return first_letter+last_letter

def firstAndLast(s):
    string=s
    first_letter=string[0]
    length=len[s]
    last_letter=string[length-1]
    return first_letter+last_letter
